StringValues.16: Once hooked, use this fireworks stand to set off a dazzling shower of fireworks! Happy New Year!
StringValues.14: The item can be placed on Yard or Roof hooks. You may only set off fireworks once every 90 seconds.

EmoteActions.Message: You may only use the Fireworks once every 90 seconds.
You marvel at the wonderous colors that spew forth from the fireworks device.
